Another trip around the sun. Livin’ the dream and these two are the reason it is so damn sweet! I’m so grateful for this ride. Lost a friend and mentor and hero last weekend but his melodic mantra will vibrate forever and I’ll do my part to keep it humming wherever i can. I have to remind myself. I have everything I need. I also want more and that’s okay! More life, more laughter, more love, and more creating…I feel an era of self love and selfless service to the greater good and the real real ones unlocked…today I woke up and told my self “i Love You,” took 10 massive breaths, gripped my toes in the grass and said “it’s on!” Love y’all…thanks Mom and Dad for crossing paths ( briefly ) and mixing up this wild elixir of a life…❤️

Hope ur spinnin #HolidaysInHawaii around the house this evening with da keiki and aunteh and unko dem! Was a pleasure to make this with my Ewa Beach braddah @braxtonolita ! We actually put real life Ewa beach ocean and vibe sounds on the record. It’s da killazzzzzzz! 

Enjoy…all jokes aside. This was a trip to a magical place while making this record. Reminding me of my connection to not only the sights and sand and ocean of the islands…but the sounds run deep through my soul! And to shine a light on a legend of a passed down tradition of the most beautiful music originating in the islands was a call of duty. Hope you dig it as much as we do

Recorded at @islandsoundstudios @coldcanyonclub @villagestudios
